CONTEXT set_ops
SETS
    S
CONSTANTS
    a b x uni intr diff pw pw1 ext rng natc intc
AXIOMS
    @axm1 a ⊆ S
    @axm2 b ⊆ S
    @axm3 x ∈ S
    @axm4 uni = a ∪ b
    @axm5 intr = a ∩ b
    @axm6 diff = a ∖ b
    @axm7 pw ∈ ℙ(S)
    @axm8 pw1 ∈ ℙ1(S)
    @axm9 ext = {x}
    @axm10 rng = 1 ‥ 10
    @axm11 natc = ℕ
    @axm12 intc = ℤ
END
